# Release Process

## Overview

Our release process uses Coolify for automated deployments and release management.

## Release Types

### 1. Feature Releases

```yaml
# Feature deployment configuration
deployment:
  type: feature
  settings:
    # Branch pattern for feature deployments
    branchPattern: feature/*
    # Auto deploy on push
    autoDeploy: true
    # Preview environment
    preview: true
    # Cleanup on PR close
    cleanup: true
```

### 2. Staging Releases

```yaml
# Staging deployment configuration
deployment:
  type: staging
  settings:
    # Branch for staging
    branch: develop
    # Auto deploy on merge
    autoDeploy: true
    # Environment variables
    environment: staging
    # Health checks
    healthCheck: true
```

### 3. Production Releases

```yaml
# Production deployment configuration
deployment:
  type: production
  settings:
    # Branch for production
    branch: main
    # Manual deployment
    autoDeploy: false
    # Environment variables
    environment: production
    # Health checks
    healthCheck: true
```

